{"tid":2192323,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Pokémon The roleplaying game (TRPG)，簡稱Pokérole招人啦！","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T07:33:06.000Z","uid":365070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f96616a0bfc66109a8b2253989906b26f046d5bc","tid":2192323,"uid":365070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"Pok&eacute;mon The roleplaying game，簡稱Pok&eacute;role招人啦！<br />\n歡迎來到Pocket Monster的世界！<br />\n這個世界裡到處充斥著Pocket Monster......簡稱「Pok&eacute;mon」的不可思議的生物！<br />\n隱藏著不可思議力量的Pok&eacute;mon們以各式各樣的姿態與我們人類一起生活著！<br />\n準備好與這些Pok&eacute;mon們邂逅、冒險、戰鬥，跟他們一起感受喜怒哀樂了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n你們首先會成為一名學生，熟悉規則及遊玩方式，當然你們還沒有搭上旅程，所以還沒有第一隻屬於自己的Pok&eacute;mon，但是你們仍然會有一場小小的冒險。<br />\n<br />\nPokerole 1E版規則<br />\n人數：3-5<br />\n形式：不連續短團(3~6小時)<br />\n風格：輕鬆小品<br />\n日期：星期一、三，偶而突發星期四、日<br />\n時間：晚上2100-2400<br />\n報名方式：留言，我會跟你聯絡。入Whatsapp群組或者找齊人直接約我也可"},{"pid":"77d1109806b03f598edf8e5f29499ab749cdff65","tid":2192323,"uid":242453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"Hello 有興趣求join"},{"pid":"02154c369a3f5dda074dd2e31385602dcfd969d5","tid":2192323,"uid":365070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d1109806b03f598edf8e5f29499ab749cdff65","tid":2192323,"uid":242453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"Hello 有興趣求join"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"朋友你要入群組正自己組團咁？"},{"pid":"26d11c493ae206897b4e80846901365034492838","tid":2192323,"uid":242453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02154c369a3f5dda074dd2e31385602dcfd969d5","tid":2192323,"uid":365070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77d1109806b03f598edf8e5f29499ab749cdff65","tid":2192323,"uid":242453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"Hello 有興趣求join"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"朋友你要入群組正自己組團咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTim